      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like an absolute dream and is basically in flawless shape. If you've been looking for 'the one,' this is definitely it! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
