    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering power with surgical precision up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a M-Variable limited-slip differential. This chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing prophylaxis. The suspension maintains factory kinematics with zero bushing deflection. A true collector-grade specimen with an immaculate undercarriage, original Laguna Seca Blue finish, and comprehensive service records detailing valve adjustments and fluid analysis.",
      "price": 46500.0,
