    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade full-body ceramic coating with zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. The factory 19-inch forged wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the black Dakota leather with blue contrast stitching remains supple, smelling fresh with absolutely no wear on the side bolsters or Alcantara steering wheel. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; all service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized BMW centers, with a complete binder of service records included. It has never seen rain, has never been tracked, and has been driven only on fair-weather weekends. Every button, screen, and mechanical component operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a collector-grade example destined for a discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
